1. Click **"Select PDF File"** → pick any PDF from your machine (even a dummy).
2. Click **"Upload & Vault"**.
3. **Expected UI:**
   - Button shows `Encrypting…` spinner for a moment
   - Alert popup: `"Paper encrypted and vaulted successfully!"`
   - **"Vaulted Papers"** section appears below with the paper at status `VAULTED`
