4. **Expected Terminal 1 log:**
```
INFO: POST /api/v1/exams/.../papers → 200
```

5. **Expected Terminal 2 (Celery) log:**
```
[Celery] Scheduling decryption tasks for paper [id], exam [id]...
[Celery] OFFLINE exam: scheduling decrypt_paper_for_print for paper [id]
```

6. **Expected Supabase checks:**
