## 8. Common Issues & Fixes

| Symptom | Cause | Fix |
|---------|-------|-----|
| Vault upload fails with 500 | Bucket missing | Create `question-papers-vault` in Supabase Storage |
| Answer sheet upload fails with 500 | Bucket missing | Create `answer-sheet-uploads` in Supabase Storage |
| 🖨 Print tab grayed out | Exam mode is ONLINE | Only for OFFLINE exams |
| 🚚 Transit tab grayed out | Exam mode is ONLINE | Only for OFFLINE exams |
| OTP box never appears | Trunk not IN_TRANSIT | Dispatch the trunk first |
| `OUTSIDE_GEOFENCE` on local test | Center has no lat/lon set | Add `latitude`, `longitude` to center row in Supabase |
| QR verify — "Invalid signature" | Wrong JWT key | Set `ADMIT_CARD_JWT_PRIVATE_KEY` in `.env` |
| Check-in fails — "No rooms available" | Room capacity reached | Add more rooms in Centers tab |
| Always `RESCAN_REQUIRED` | Random AI mock (~15% fail rate) | Re-upload; it's probabilistic — try again |
| Command Center shows no alerts | No ingest called | Use the PowerShell ingest command in Step F |
